\v 12 Jini xibajob ti' c'ajtibe JesÃºs: Xiq'uiyon lojon majlel ya' ba'an chityam. Ac'ÊŒyon lojon ochel ti chityam, che' ti yÊŒlÊŒ jini xibajob.
