\v 27 Ti queji i yubin bajche' chÊŒncol i cha'len JesÃºs. Che' jini ti tyÊŒli ti' pat JesÃºs ya' ba' much'quibil quixtyaÃ±ujob. Ti' tyÊŒlbe i pislel JesÃºs.
