\v 28 Ti' bajÃ±el Ã±a'tyÊŒ: Mi jin jach i pislel mic tyÊŒlben, jasÊŒl mic lajmel. Che' ti' Ã±a'tyÊŒ jini c'am bÊŒ x'ixic.
