\v 43 JesÃºs ti' wen tiq'uiyob cha'an mach quejic i subeÃ±ob yaÃ±o' bÊŒ. Ti' subeyob cha'an i we'saÃ±ob jini xc'alÊŒl.
\c 6
\s1 Ya'an JesÃºs ti Nazaret
