\v 4 JesÃºs ti' subeyob: Jini mu' bÊŒ i xiq'ue' yÊŒle' Dios ma' mi q'uejlel ti Ã±uc ti' lumal ya' ba'an i pi'ÊŒlob, ya' ti yotyot. Ti yan tyac jach bÊŒ lum mi q'uejlel ti Ã±uc. Che' ti yÊŒlÊŒ JesÃºs.
