\v 5 Mach'an ti mejli i pÊŒse' mi jump'ejlic Ã±uc bÊŒ i p'ÊŒtyÊŒlel JesÃºs ya'i. Jin jach ti' tyÊŒlbeyob i bÊŒc'tyal cha'tiquil uxtiquil c'amo' bÊŒ. Ti' c'oq'uisÊŒyob.
