\v 7 JesÃºs ti' pÊŒyÊŒ jini doce ajcÊŒnt'aÃ±ob i cha'an. Cha'cha'tiquil ti' xiq'ui majlel. Ti yÊŒq'ueyob i p'ÊŒtyÊŒlel cha'an i choc tyacob loq'uel xibajob.
