\v 8 Ti' subeyob cha'an mach'ic i niq'ui ch'ÊŒmob majlel ya' ti bij. Jin jach mi' ch'ÊŒmob majlel i Ã±ÊŒ' tye'. Mach yom i ch'ÊŒmob majlel i morral mi wajobic, mi tyaq'uiÃ±obic.
