\v 13 Ti' chocoyob loq'uel cabÊŒl xibajob je'el. Ti yulbeyob aceite cabÊŒl c'am'o' bÊŒ. Ti' lajmisÊŒyob.
\s1 Ti tsÊŒnsÊŒnti Juan tsa' bÊŒ i yÊŒc'ÊŒ ch'ÊŒm ja'
\r (Mt. 14.1-12; Lc. 9.7-9)
\p 
\v 14 Jini Ã±uc bÊŒ yumÊŒl Herodes bÊŒ i c'aba' ti yubi chÊŒ bÊŒ ti' cha'le JesÃºs, como pejtyelel ti' wen cÊŒmbeyob bajche' ti' cha'le. Jin cha'an Herodes ti lolon alÊŒ: JiÃ±ÊŒch jini Juan tsa' bÊŒ i yÊŒc'ÊŒ ch'ÊŒm ja' ti cha' tyejchi loq'uel ya' ba'an sajtyemo' bÊŒ. Jin cha'an mi tsictiyel i p'ÊŒtyÊŒlel ti toÃ±el, che' ti lolon alÊŒ Herodes.
