\v 1 JesÃºs ti' subeyob: Melel mic subeÃ±etla, cha'tiquil uxtiquil wÊŒ' bÊŒ aÃ±ob mach'an mi quej i sajtyelob jintyo mi' Ã±axan ilaÃ±ob che' mi quej i yumintyel Dios ti' p'ÊŒtyÊŒlel. Che' ti yÊŒlÊŒ JesÃºs.
