\v 1 JesÃºs ti queji i pejcaÃ±ob ti lajoÃ±el tyac. Ti yÊŒlÊŒ: An juntiquil winic tsa' bÊŒ pÊŒc'ÊŒ ts'ujsub. Ti' joy corrajli. Ti' chajpÊŒ i yajnib ba' mi' pets'beÃ±ob loq'uel i ya'lel. Ti' ts'ÊŒpÊŒ chan bÊŒ i wa'lib cha'an i q'uintyan paÃ±imil. Che' jini ti yÊŒc'ÊŒ ti' majÃ±ÊŒntyel ajcÊŒÃ±ÊŒtya ts'ujsubob. Ti majli ti Ã±ajt bÊŒ paÃ±imil.
