\v 18 Ti' lÊŒc'ÊŒyob JesÃºs cha'tiquil uxtiquil saduceojob. JiÃ±ÊŒch mu' bÊŒ i yÊŒlob cha'an mach'an mi lac cha' tyejchel loq'uel ba'an sajtyemo' bÊŒ. Ti' c'ajtibeyob JesÃºs:
