\v 19 Maestro, MoisÃ©s ti yÊŒq'ueyonla mandar chÊŒ bÊŒ yom i cha'len mi ti sajti juntiquil winic mi ti' bajÃ±el cÊŒyÊŒ yijÃ±am che' max tyo ba'an yalobil. Ti yÊŒlÊŒ yom i wersa pÊŒyben yijÃ±am yÊŒscun jini ijts'iÃ±ÊŒl bÊŒ cha'an mi' tyejchben i jiÃ±ÊŒjlel jini tsa' bÊŒ sajti. Che' ti yÊŒlÊŒ MoisÃ©s, che'ob.
