\v 20 Che' jini, an siete winicob yoque yijts'iÃ±ob i bÊŒ. Ti' pÊŒyÊŒ yijÃ±am jini ascuÃ±ÊŒl bÊŒ. Ti sajti che' max tyo ba'an i yalobil.
