\v 21 Ti' tsÊŒtsÊŒ subeyob juntiquil ya' bÊŒ an ya'i cha'an i q'ueche' majlel i cruzil JesÃºs. JiÃ±ÊŒch SimÃ³n bÊŒ i c'aba', ya' ch'oyol ti yambÊŒ paÃ±imil Cirene bÊŒ i c'aba', c'otyel muc' ti matye'el. JiÃ±ÊŒch i tyat Alejandro yic'ot Rufo.
