\v 35 Che' Ã±ac ti yubiyob cha'tiquil uxtiquil ya' bÊŒ wa'alob ti yÊŒlÊŒyob: Ubinla, chÊŒncox i pÊŒye' tyÊŒlel ElÃ­as tsa' bÊŒ xiq'ui i yÊŒle' Dios, che'ob.
